about.summary: Backport of functools.lru_cache from Python 3.3 as published at ActiveState.

name: backports.functools_lru_cache
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "backports.functools_lru_cache" %}
{% set version = "1.2.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1c20e07f1a8a36a19d5d258b6b076e588d78d8fc7c2c4487ffe3a280f55a7bd1

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - setuptools_scm

  run:
    - python
    - setuptools

test:
  imports:
    - backports.functools_lru_cache

about:
  home: https://github.com/jaraco/backports.functools_lru_cache
  license: MIT
  summary: 'Backport of functools.lru_cache from Python 3.3 as published at ActiveState.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mariusvniekerk
